{"word":"H4319 - מִיכָהוּ - Mîykâhûw - me-kaw'-hoo - Micaiah","slug":"H4319","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִיכָהוּ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Mîykâhûw"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>me-kaw'-hoo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Micaiah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>מיכהוּ</he> o</b> <p />Transliteration: <b>mı̂ykâhû</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>me-kaw'-hoo</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Michaiah = \"who is like God\" <ol><li>son of Imlah and a prophet of Samaria who predicted the defeat and death of king Ahab of Israel</li></ol> <p />Origin: a contr. for <a href=\"#/H4321\">H4321</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4310\">H4310</a>, <a href=\"#/H4311\">H4311</a>, <a href=\"#/H4316\">H4316</a>, <a href=\"#/H4317\">H4317</a>, <a href=\"#/H4318\">H4318</a>, <a href=\"#/H4320\">H4320</a>, <a href=\"#/H4321\">H4321</a>, <a href=\"#/H4322\">H4322</a>, <a href=\"#/H4323\">H4323</a>, <a href=\"#/H4324\">H4324</a>, <a href=\"#/H4326\">H4326</a>, <a href=\"#/H4332\">H4332</a>, <a href=\"#/H4509\">H4509</a>"}]}